Add_Dynamic_Module Mechanics Bananas_Standard_Mechanics
Add_Dynamic_Module Physics Appeal_Jolt_Physics
Add_Dynamic_Module AI Appeal_Recast_BehaviorTree_AI

Mechanics Debug 1
Physics Debug 1
AI Debug 1

Mechanics Use Player Default
Mechanics Set Player Mode OnFoot
Mechanics Analog Player Move_Forward 24000
Mechanics Digital Player Jump
Mechanics Update Player

Physics Use Player Default
Physics Set_Body_Type Player Character
Physics Set Player Mass 80
Physics Set_Position Player 0.0 1.0 0.0
Physics Apply_Impulse Player 1.0 0.0 0.0
Physics Update Player

AI Use Guard Default
AI Set Guard Target Player
AI Event Guard PlayerSeen
AI Think Guard
AI Decide Guard

AI Release Guard
Physics Release Player
Mechanics Release Player
Done
